 Ekene Som Mekwunye AMVCA Winner makes his directing debut in a feature film with the movie titled Light In The Dark. The movie is a Romance thriller which stars Rita Dominic, Joke Silva, Kalu Ikeagwu, Saidi Balogun, Ngozi Nwosu, Kiki Omeili, Bimbo Ademoye, Mannie of CoolFM and a lot of other awesome actors. It will be in cinemas nationwide from Friday, January 25th, 2019.  (BELLA NAIJA) 